{"search_data": "UttarakhandUttarakhand Deendayal Upadhyay Kisan Kalyan Yojana \u2013 Soft Loans for FarmersUttarakhand govt. launches Deendayal Upadhyay Kisan Kalyan Yojana 2019 to provide soft loans upto Rs. 1 lakh to small & marginal farmers at just 2% interest rate with repayment period of 3 years \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Uttarakhand Deendayal Upadhyay Kisan Kalyan Yojana 2019To give a major boost to the agricultural sector and to raise the living standards of farmers, govt. will start 2 new schemes. The name of these two schemes are Integrated Cooperative Development Scheme & Deendayal Upadhyay Kisan Kalyan Yojana. These schemes will be inaugurated by PM Narendra Modi to realize the vision of Doubling Farmers Income by 2022.Under this Deen Dayal Upadhyay Sehkarita Kisan Kalyan Yojana, govt. will provide farm loans upto Rs. 1 lakh at just 2% interest rate. All the farmers will have to make repayment of the loan amount within a duration of 3 years. The compounding charges would be imposed after 1 year on the farmer for non-payment of the loan amount.This information has been taken from official website \u2013 http://uttarainformation.gov.in. Along with improving financial conditions of the farmers, this scheme would help in strengthening the rural economy along with check forced migration from the hills.\u092a\u094d\u0930\u0927\u093e\u0928\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0936\u094d\u0930\u0940 @narendramodi, \u0906\u091c \u0930\u0941\u0926\u094d\u0930\u092a\u0941\u0930, \u090a\u0927\u092e\u0938\u093f\u0902\u0939\u0928\u0917\u0930 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u20b93340 \u0915\u0930\u094b\u0921\u093c \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u092e\u0947\u0915\u093f\u0924 \u0938\u0939\u0915\u093e\u0930\u0940 \u0935\u093f\u0915\u093e\u0938 \u092a\u0930\u093f\u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u090f\u0935\u0902 \u0926\u0940\u0928\u0926\u092f\u093e\u0932 \u0909\u092a\u093e\u0927\u094d\u092f\u093e\u092f \u0938\u0939\u0915\u093e\u0930\u093f\u092